{"tid":1506004,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"涉性侵國中女！男遭剝光動私刑　辣椒水噴下體痛慘","createTime":"2019-08-25T16:38:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-25T21:08:26.000Z","uid":2002,"like":36,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"146dfc0bf91273b1c3c9fa8580a0c3c97bef13cd","tid":1506004,"uid":2002,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T16:38:01.000Z","msg":"桃園市1名張姓男子涉嫌性侵13歲國中少女，訊後遭警方函送地檢署偵辦，事後獲交保候傳；沒想到，被害人親友心有不甘，竟將張男帶往偏僻處教訓，不僅把他剝光痛毆，還朝其下體噴灑辣椒水，私刑影片在網路瘋傳。據悉，警方已掌握所有涉案人身分並陸續傳喚到案，全案將以妨害自由等罪嫌送辦。<br />\n<br />\n 據了解，臉書社團近日流傳一段長約2分多鐘的私刑影片，只見1名男子全身赤裸，遭10多名年輕男子毆打，下體也被噴灑辣椒水，痛得他哇哇大叫、不斷求饒，但涉嫌動私刑的一夥人未因此善罷干休，仍不停在旁大聲喝斥，除大罵「敢強姦13歲小女生」，更喝令男子喊出自己的姓名和住址。"},{"pid":"7f28bde7c7c0472030b2bdc082f5872f28336024","tid":1506004,"uid":2002,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T16:38:41.000Z","msg":"「鄉民的正義」？強姦犯被目擊者毆打致死還砍下睪丸<br />\n<br />\n〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕南非象牙公園內，3名男子被居民指控強姦2名少女多次，被目擊民眾動用私刑毆打，其中2名嫌犯趁亂逃跑，一名嫌犯被圍毆致死，還被砍下生殖器。<br />\n<br />\n綜合媒體報導，嫌犯強姦兩名在象牙公園散步的少女，用刀與槍強逼她們就範，3名男子對少女性侵多次，2名少女分別14歲及18歲，當地居民目擊這起可怕的事件，決定自己來「伸張正義」，追捕這3名嫌犯，其中2名嫌犯趁亂逃跑，被逮到的嫌犯不僅被毆打、凌虐致死，還被砍下睪丸，下場相當淒慘。<br />\n<br />\n報導指出，當地警方表示，2名女孩面對持刀和槍枝的嫌犯被反覆強姦多次，但是不認為居民動用私刑制裁嫌犯的行為是正確的，警方警告民眾「不要自己進行制裁行為」，目前警方正在追捕2名逃亡的強姦犯，但未逮捕任何動用私刑的居民"},{"pid":"a3351eed271cbab21bbc7f14c2192f2a95cb9de4","tid":1506004,"uid":2002,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T16:39:51.000Z","msg":"【泰抵打】29歲色魔圖姦孕婦 遭過路青年打到變豬頭 影相放上fb<br />\n<br />\n泰國日前發生男子企圖強姦孕婦案件，幸一班路過現場的「正義哥」出手救人，孕婦幸無大礙，而救人者對色魔濫用私刑，有機會被追究責任。<br />\n<br />\n案件於周三（24日）晚發生，當時23歲孕婦獨自回家，遭29歲男子拉到草叢企圖強姦，縱使事主大喊自己懷孕，對方仍未收手。此時一班青年行經現場，聽到呼救聲後挺身捉住色魔，當場把他暴打一輪後交給警方，其後更把色魔的照片上載到facebook，引來逾1.8萬網讚好。警方指疑犯被打到顴骨裂開、顱內出血，其傷勢涉及私刑，有權對施暴者追究法律責任。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2731132/org/9bee619d988ba722334230384c70f273.jpg/PMOWSPjZVGiv9tWFpoDi827lkeQ79sBZt5KmVbeSplU\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2731132%2Forg%2F9bee619d988ba722334230384c70f273.jpg%2FPMOWSPjZVGiv9tWFpoDi827lkeQ79sBZt5KmVbeSplU&h=bfa31aed&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4e6a50fffb5663945bd6a7d173343b39787d97cd","tid":1506004,"uid":2002,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T16:40:11.000Z","msg":"大家識做啦"},{"pid":"25abd62763b436950b9b08726a08b7fcf1659ce5","tid":1506004,"uid":236646,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T16:40:41.000Z","msg":"強姦犯是沒有無辜的"},{"pid":"c46b988add5935c4d075d63478320b95f45326df","tid":1506004,"uid":2002,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T16:41:06.000Z","msg":"美國59歲男姦殺8歲女孩 入獄後被室友動「私刑」活活打死<br />\n<br />\n綜合外媒報道，59歲的Anthony Palma 2年前因姦殺一名8歲女童被判終身監禁，至今仍未找到女童屍身。有關當局本來打算今年再審訊他，問出埋屍地點，豈料他已被同牢房、因謀殺罪被判終身監禁的Raymond Pillado打死。<br />\n<br />\n獄警指，當時Palma被一張毛毯蓋著，面朝地板。當掀起毛毯時，只見整地都是血，Palma亦失去呼吸。據法醫驗屍報告顯示，Palma遭到鈍器重擊受傷，並遭勒頸窒息而死。警方相信Pillado之所以會將他打死，是因為不滿他是個性侵殺人犯，所以趁著同牢房，將他殺死。"},{"pid":"94c34c50f5fdcf63fb74dc6aa847e438085279ad","tid":1506004,"uid":200083,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T16:41:11.000Z","msg":"咁暴力架？ 千祈唔好有樣學樣對藍屍咁做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"449bf26ad5b6090f298f813f24efde9975afa96e","tid":1506004,"uid":2002,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T16:41:42.000Z","msg":"利伸 支持和平理性 反對暴力行為"},{"pid":"2d4a3ac74171efa5a33b3155e47367260e790148","tid":1506004,"uid":2002,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T16:44:31.000Z","msg":"日日出街帶枝白花油<br />\n呢排好多蚊"},{"pid":"5a11af861ed655d344e25cd07eb0b97c806bc795","tid":1506004,"uid":48796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T16:45:57.000Z","msg":"治癒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"adc439b672286b6c9ad128a146a876f130ed1017","tid":1506004,"uid":199532,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T16:51:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e9f7b8d444ec0a75fd255e89f8eba52c462977a","tid":1506004,"uid":239496,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"94c34c50f5fdcf63fb74dc6aa847e438085279ad","tid":1506004,"uid":200083,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T16:41:11.000Z","msg":"咁暴力架？ 千祈唔好有樣學樣對藍屍咁做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T16:59:37.000Z","msg":"荃灣、北角、元朗"},{"pid":"f4766b348930c9767a4523d5ad40983f97157933","tid":1506004,"uid":2002,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T17:00:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"185e9bc9727cdf4a5e6e75df7ce31761120bb625","tid":1506004,"uid":285826,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T18:14:33.000Z","msg":"敢做就要預比人爆蛋！"},{"pid":"0ce3951976e6edc61554bfe5ea9568fd0538e914","tid":1506004,"uid":197640,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T20:52:01.000Z","msg":"辣椒水咪算小兒科，wasbi 你仲仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b0ac409e01330801a39c3225198410de74dba95d","tid":1506004,"uid":65210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T20:56:58.000Z","msg":"［開飯/住宿/義診/搵工］你班前線死廢青 未成年中學雞同我入黎！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1503091\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1503091</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"2e6b1b90a9eadefa9bc433538905d47e286acd12","tid":1506004,"uid":230821,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T21:01:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/jj.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"641cadba04ea0752556ed2b03bebc7f6060bbeb9","tid":1506004,"uid":113115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T21:04:12.000Z","msg":"私刑係popo<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ddd710eec4a60f77449d8db0503b0d03fec5672","tid":1506004,"uid":294555,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T21:06:30.000Z","msg":"以後克警比清算我估後果都會係獄中死<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />你地放心去啦 大嫂我會幫你地照顧"},{"pid":"c8e965fd749a1ab4e3c6ee7f911a6977e1bec9c5","tid":1506004,"uid":291626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T21:08:26.000Z","msg":"雙飛人 落去傷口都好勁 千祈唔好咁做呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}